data.description: This property is currently a self-managed short-term vacation rental with a rental history of $37k in 2022 and tracking the same for 2023. EVERYTHING STAYS including the HOT TUB, so it's rental ready, if that is the intent! This property is a short drive from Navarre Beach, shopping, local eateries, and recreational activities. Sitting on a 1/2 acre, there is plenty of room to add a pool or add more outdoor activities. Whether you want this property as a primary residence or income producing rental, don't miss your chance to own a great property. Seller will re-roof with acceptable offer.
